ezvcard.parameter

Class VCardParameters.VCardParameterList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

    Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    VCardParameters.EnumParameterList
    Enclosing class:
    VCardParameters

    public abstract class VCardParameters.VCardParameterList<T>
extends AbstractList<T>

    A list that converts the raw string values of a parameter to another kind of value (for example, Integers).

    This list is backed by the VCardParameters object. Any changes made to the list will affect the VCardParameters object and vice versa.

    If a String value cannot be converted to the appropriate data type, an IllegalStateException is thrown.
